events.name: 後ろから開けるドア（単

parameters: It seems to be locked from the other side.
Yui: "Geez! It's your fault I got scolded!"
Takumi: "I got carried away because I was so excited..."

Yui: "What's that supposed to mean? You're acting different than usual
and it's throwing me off!"
Takumi: "Then, let's go to the pool together!"
Yui: "How many times do I have to tell you I'm not going..."

Polka: "I've detected a strong energy from the south of the Fols
district!"

Yui: "(The south of the Fols district... Isn't that where the pool
is!?)"
Yui: "Of all places, why does it have to be the pool!!"

Takumi: "Why? Didn't I tell you earlier? I wanted to go with you
because today is the opening day."
Yui: "Sorry, Takumi-kun. Please don't bother with me anymore..."
Takumi: "Tch, I was so close. Maybe I rushed it a bit..."
Takumi: "That panic... Could it be that a Zaidargg has appeared?"
